# The website image installs composer + yarn deps at build time and stashes them
# in named volumes. A stale vendor/node_modules inside the copied ./data/ context
# shadows that fresh install (composer sees packages already present and skips
# reinstall, so composer-patches never runs) and bloats the build context.
data/vendor/
data/node_modules/
data/.git

# Same, for the blue-green "green" checkout (see Dockerfile ARG DATA_DIR).
data-green/vendor/
data-green/node_modules/
data-green/.git
